{"type":"message","id":"0b9206c9","parentId":"ff5eb7cb","timestamp":"2026-04-16T03:12:47.895Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user sent a link to a Feishu app (miaoda.feishu.cn/app/app_4jrrrk3up2qfr?agentId=main) and mentioned they need to scan a QR code to log in. Then they asked if the server is congested again, and now they're asking \"又咋了\" (what happened now).\n\nLet me first fetch the URL to see what the website looks like, and also check if there are any issues with the server. Let me try to access the link."},{"type":"text","text":"没堵，我来看看这个网站。\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_bdykhhdpro60_1","name":"web_fetch","arguments":{"url":"https://miaoda.feishu.cn/app/app_4jrrrk3up2qfr?agentId=main","maxChars":5000}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776309159274,"responseId":"062f86a878636cc25ed8d63c15a0f277"}}
