{"type":"message","id":"270873ce","parentId":"df2c4c40","timestamp":"2026-04-16T03:13:22.005Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"VibeSurf is not running. I need to let the user know. I can't run it myself (as per the skill instructions). The user needs to run `vibesurf` to start it.\n\nBut wait - for screen scraping a Feishu app that requires login, even a browser won't help much since I'd need to be authenticated as the user. Let me think about what the user actually needs.\n\nThe user wants to replicate a website's frontend. For a Feishu app that requires login, the best approach would be:\n1. If they have the app's source code/front-end code - they can share that\n2. If they just want to see the UI - they could take screenshots\n\n\n3. For replicating the frontend, I'd need either screen recordings or screenshots of the different views, mockup data or API documentation, and ideally access to any design specs or wireframes they might have. Without one of these, I'm limited in how much I can actually help."},{"type":"text","text":"VibeSurf 浏览器没开，你先跑一下 `vibesurf` 把它启动起来。\n\n不过说实话——复刻飞书内部应用，光靠截图不够。我需要：\n\n1. **你能给我导出发送的内容/截图**——把主要页面的样子发给我\n2. **或者告诉我这是什么类型的应用**——审批？表单？文档？社区？\n\n你对这个应用本身了解多少？是你们自己开发的，还是第三方 SaaS？"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776309189837,"responseId":"062f86c657ee44ea8203159a5bde9462"}}
