{"type":"message","id":"a557d657","parentId":"2e16d103","timestamp":"2026-04-16T03:14:12.884Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"System: [2026-04-16 11:14:10 GMT+8] Feishu[kiit] DM | ou_f590c429b7ded95568bebca2f534efdb [msg:om_x100b51310ed4e488c3d4f5c7e1c2b31]\n\nConversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"message_id\": \"om_x100b51310ed4e488c3d4f5c7e1c2b31\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"ou_f590c429b7ded95568bebca2f534efdb\",\n  \"sender\": \"ou_f590c429b7ded95568bebca2f534efdb\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Thu 2026-04-16 11:14 GMT+8\"\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"ou_f590c429b7ded95568bebca2f534efdb\",\n  \"id\": \"ou_f590c429b7ded95568bebca2f534efdb\",\n  \"name\": \"ou_f590c429b7ded95568bebca2f534efdb\"\n}\n```\n\n用vibesurf 你能全程自己搞定吗"}],"timestamp":1776309252871}}
{"type":"message","id":"1b275ae8","parentId":"a557d657","timestamp":"2026-04-16T03:14:32.523Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is asking if I can use VibeSurf to handle the entire task of copying a website frontend on my own. Let me think about this.\n\nThe task is:\n1. Go to a Feishu internal app (which requires login)\n2. Analyze its UI\n3. Recreate the frontend\n\nVibeSurf is a browser automation tool. But the issue is:\n1. VibeSurf is not currently running (we just checked)\n2. The app requires login/authentication\n3. Even if I could access it, analyzing and reproducing a frontend requires understanding the structure, not just visual elements\n\nLet me think more carefully about what \"全程自己搞定\" means:\n\n\nIf VibeSurf were running, I could automate the browser to log in and navigate through the app, then analyze the page structure and visual design to create a recreation. But there are real limitations here - the login would require the user's credentials or session cookies, and understanding the full UI would need more than just visual inspection. Plus, actually recreating a complex app frontend is quite different from just navigating it.\n\nI should give the user an honest assessment of what's actually feasible versus what sounds possible in theory."},{"type":"text","text":"说实话，有两个硬坎：\n\n**1. 浏览器我能控制** ✅\nVibeSurf 跑起来之后，我可以自动化操作——登录、截图、分析页面结构。\n\n**2. 但复刻本身不是自动的** ⚠️\n\"复刻\"是把看到的 UI 用代码重写出来。这需要：\n- 视觉还原（我能看出用了什么颜色、间距、字体）\n- 结构理解（我能读 HTML 标签和 CSS）\n- 代码实现（我可以直接写 HTML/CSS/React）\n\n**关键问题**：这个飞书应用是你们自己开发的，还是从市场上安装的第三方应用？\n\n- **自己开发的** → 你有源码，直接改源码比复刻快\n- **第三方 SaaS** → 只能抄外观，但功能逻辑抄不了（API 在别人手里）\n\n另外，\"全程\"的前提是你先把 VibeSurf 启动起来。你跑一下 `vibesurf`，然后告诉我。"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776309252897,"