{"type":"message","id":"9dd118b6","parentId":"678fc7dd","timestamp":"2026-04-16T03:16:04.728Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"HALEI just wants the frontend UI, doesn't need the backend. This is a \"clone the UI\" task. \n\nLet me think about what I can do here. The key steps would be:\n1. Launch VibeSurf browser to see the actual app\n2. Take screenshots and extract the page structure\n3. Build the frontend\n\nThe challenge is that this is a Feishu internal app that requires login. HALEI would need to scan a QR code or log in. \n\nI can use VibeSurf to navigate and take screenshots once it's running. But the initial login/QE code scanning is tricky - I'd need HALEI to do that part, or share their screen.\n\n\nI should respond confirming I can handle the frontend cloning once I have access to the app through VibeSurf, and ask them to start it up so I can begin capturing the UI."},{"type":"text","text":"明白，只抄前端，这事能搞。\n\n流程是这样：\n\n1. 你启动 `vibesurf`（浏览器）\n2. 我自动化操作 → 截图 + 提取页面结构\n3. 我写出 HTML/CSS/React 前端代码\n\n**但有一个问题**：飞书应用需要登录，QR 码你得帮我扫。这个只能你在自己机器上操作，没法远程代劳。\n\n---\n\n你先把 `vibesurf` 跑起来，我这边随时待命。跑起来之后告诉我，我来接手下一步。"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776309350835,"responseId":"062f87672a2bb6e2e9c7dd5449dfc38d"}}
